{"tid":208914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（特發）特朗普：「韓國曾是中國的一部分」","createTime":"2017-04-19T22:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T01:18:15.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c48182d2889532e9f769dbeca1029fd28ef9e2b","tid":208914,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T22:56:00.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普又語出驚人了！這次他說的是「韓國是中國的一部分」，這番言論引起韓國人民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n川普與習近平在4月6日、7日一連進行2天會談，不過川普在12日接受華爾街日報採訪時，卻說出「韓國是中國的一部分」的驚人之語。<br />\n<br />\n川普提到，習近平在會面中提到中國與韓國的歷史，川普特別強調這邊所說的韓國並不是指北韓，而是整個朝鮮半島，因為「韓國曾是中國的一部分」。<br />\n<br />\n不過這個說法到底是出自習近平的口中，抑或者是川普自己的想法並未獲得證實。美國線上新聞媒體Quartz則批評川普做了令人震驚的無知發言。<br />\n<br />\nQuartz也提到，歷史中有兩段期間韓國可能被誤解成中國的一部分，一個是漢朝漢武帝曾征服北朝鮮，並設立了漢四郡，另一個就是蒙古帝國在13世紀征伐朝鮮半島，讓當時的高麗國成為元朝的屬國。不過韓國屬於中國一部份的說法，並不被大多數的歷史學家接受。<br />\n----<br />\n元朝版圖可能真係連埋高麗，唔怪得南韓話張三豐係韓國人啦"},{"pid":"124d8c8efedd3465d1d953802596ef730139bb96","tid":208914,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T23:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c587ce9ab708aa94d85211c02a6f4badcafdf0","tid":208914,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T23:03:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">曾是.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b9935c039fc8c6916211d41751ec74f9c8dac25e","tid":208914,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T23:18:51.000Z","msg":"討好中國"},{"pid":"b082ab20cf525c699394ad696479cb11bd7620c0","tid":208914,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:16:43.000Z","msg":"支那曾是蒙古一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24358ac98010bc48c5fb54c3bb968e49c111ed7d","tid":208914,"uid":76637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:17:44.000Z","msg":"自古以來？"},{"pid":"9f4b6bf75199bd32d87ffc9cba5697123da642e6","tid":208914,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:18:15.000Z","msg":"蒙古被中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}